videos.title: IVF Round Two Isn't Going How We Hoped
videos.description:
Learn Italian the fun way with Lingopie! 7-day free trial + 55% OFF yearly plan.
https://learn.lingopie.com/the_pasinis

We're in our second egg retrieval round in the US and things aren't going exactly as we hoped. Unfortunately, it looks like Jessi's endometriosis is growing and that she might have an endometrioma on the right ovary. In our first egg retrieval, we were able to get 7 mature eggs and we were hoping for the same or close to it for this round, but the follicles are less and growing slower. Still praying every day and hoping for the best! Egg retrieval day is coming soon! Then only one more egg retrieval round before we can make embryos. 

Thank you for all of your love and support! Don't forget to subscribe and turn on the bell so you never miss a new video! You can also follow us on our other socials below! Ciao for now! -Jessi and Alessio

videos.title: WILL THIS SALAD SEND ME INTO LABOR?!
videos.description:
At 39 weeks pregnant, I‚Äôm officially ready to meet this baby‚Äîso, I tried the legendary Maternity Salad from Caioti Pizza Caf√© in Studio City!
This salad has become famous for putting pregnant women into labor‚Äîyes, really. Mamas from all over have made the trip to try it‚Ä¶ and some even claim they went into labor hours later. So naturally, I had to see what the hype is about!
In this vlog, I take you along for the full experience‚Äîordering the salad, eating it, reacting to the taste, and (of course) waiting to see if baby decides it‚Äôs go time.
